    <div class="overlay" id="overlay">
        <div class="videoBox">
            <div class="surpriseCard" id="surpriseCard">
                üíå Pe <b>14 februarie</b> te a»ôteaptƒÉ o surprizƒÉ...<br>
                DƒÉ-mi adresa ta »ôi √Æ»õi trimit un z√¢mbet √Æn plus ‚ù§Ô∏è
            </div>

            <video id="fwVideo" playsinline controls>
                <source src="fireworks.webm" type="video/webm">
